    <div class="section" id="an-ecosystem-for-trusted-data-sharing">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title wide">
          <h3 class="medium-heading">An Ecosystem for Trusted Data Sharing<br></h3>
          <p class="text-large">Emerging cryptographic web technologies enable secure identity and data verification
            between parties, providing a more streamlined and privacy preserving Web. Digital Bazaar’s technology
            ecosystem represents over a decade of software development, inventing and vetting technologies, and
            spearheading Web Standards at the World Wide Web Consortium.<br></p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-layout-grid blurb-grid">
          <div class="centered-grid-item"><img src="60733677c5e7cddb582e7bf0/60733677c5e7cd33432e7ced_networking.svg"
              width="256" alt="Decentralized Identity" class="icon-large">
            <h4 class="blurb-title">Decentralized Identity<br></h4>
            <div>Verifiable Credentials enable a Web of trust with no central authority. Decentralized identity puts
              people and organizations at the center of their identity management and scales to the Web.<br></div>
          </div>
          <div class="centered-grid-item"><img
              src="60733677c5e7cddb582e7bf0/608af61ce5705dd848b7edd8_database-security.svg" alt="Secure Data Management"
              class="icon-large">
            <h4 class="blurb-title">Secure Data Management<br></h4>
            <div>Encrypted Data Vaults and fit-for-purpose distributed ledgers can be leveraged to meet the secure data
              management requirements of many use cases across market verticals.<br></div>
          </div>
          <div class="centered-grid-item"><img src="60733677c5e7cddb582e7bf0/608691ad959e2740b85317ae_intersection.svg"
              alt="Integrations" class="icon-large">
            <h4 class="blurb-title">Integrations<br></h4>
            <div>We help you integrate emerging decentralized identity and data management technologies with your
              systems without having to do extensive overhauls.<br></div>
          </div>
