    <div class="section bg-gray" id="case-studies">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h6 class="subheading text-primary-1">Case Studies</h6>
          <h3 class="medium-heading">Our Technology Implementations<br></h3>
          <p>In 2014 Digital Bazaar initiated foundational Web Standards that support the decentralized identity
            ecosystem. We’ve since proven the technology via multiple Proof of Concepts involving fortune 500 companies
            and multiple national governments and are now deploying large scale production solutions into the market.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-dyn-list">
  <div role="list" class="w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="case-card w-dyn-item"><a href="/case-studies/solving-privacy-preserving-age-verification-for-150-000-convenience-stores/" class="w-inline-block"><img alt=""
