          class="case-thumb"></a>
      <div class="card-body case-study-card-body">
        <h4>Solving Privacy-preserving Age Verification for 150,000+ Convenience Stores</h4>
        <p class="case-study-card-excerpt">With a reach of 200 Million end-customers, our solution verifies a customer’s age with a high degree of accuracy.</p>
        <a href="/case-studies/solving-privacy-preserving-age-verification-for-150-000-convenience-stores/">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div><div role="listitem" class="case-card w-dyn-item"><a href="/case-studies/veres-one-a-globally-interoperable-distributed-ledger-for-decentralized-identifiers/" class="w-inline-block"><img alt=""
          src="/60733677c5e7cdbc4a2e7bf5/60869350c7b29da3e67dddd0_globalisation-3390877_1920.jpg"
          sizes="(max-width: 479px) 92vw, (max-width: 767px) 94vw, (max-width: 991px) 95vw, 46vw"
          srcset="/60733677c5e7cdbc4a2e7bf5/60869350c7b29da3e67dddd0_globalisation-3390877_1920-p-500.jpeg 500w, /60733677c5e7cdbc4a2e7bf5/60869350c7b29da3e67dddd0_globalisation-3390877_1920-p-800.jpeg 800w, /60733677c5e7cdbc4a2e7bf5/60869350c7b29da3e67dddd0_globalisation-3390877_1920-p-1080.jpeg 1080w, /60733677c5e7cdbc4a2e7bf5/60869350c7b29da3e67dddd0_globalisation-3390877_1920-p-1600.jpeg 1600w, /60733677c5e7cdbc4a2e7bf5/60869350c7b29da3e67dddd0_globalisation-3390877_1920.jpg 1920w"
          class="case-thumb"></a>
      <div class="card-body case-study-card-body">
        <h4>Veres One: A Globally Interoperable Distributed Ledger for Decentralized Identifiers</h4>
        <p class="case-study-card-excerpt">Digital Bazaar engineered the Veres One distributed ledger for the Veres One Foundation.</p>
        <a href="/case-studies/veres-one-a-globally-interoperable-distributed-ledger-for-decentralized-identifiers/">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div><div role="listitem" class="case-card w-dyn-item"><a href="/case-studies/digital-permanent-resident-cards-and-enterprise-credential-lifecycle-management/" class="w-inline-block"><img alt=""
